{
  "chapter": 55,
  "chapter_summary": "本章标题\"荡妇\"，围绕林仙儿展开三条线索。开篇林仙儿与上官金虹在暗室中密谈，上官金虹命令她去杀阿飞，透露李寻欢已被龙啸云出卖并落入掌控。林仙儿分析龙啸云借刀杀人、欲与上官金虹结拜的企图，上官金虹则轻蔑表示结义兄弟亦可出卖，同时称赞龙啸云之子龙小云人小鬼大。随后林仙儿出屋嘲讽守候在外的荆无命。场景转至如云客栈，龙小云在包房中以暴虐方式对待送来的女子。林仙儿伪装成少女进入其房，识破后两人以长辈与晚辈身份交谈，林仙儿以美色挑逗龙小云套取情报。章末林仙儿内心独白揭示她对李寻欢的复杂情感——既想毁掉他，又不愿他死在上官金虹手上。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "有时我总忍不住想要问你一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你为什么不问？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你究竟真的是个人？是不是铁打的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你感觉不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你若真是个人，为什么永远不会累？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你受不了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你认为我会求饶？你为何不再试试？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "现在不行！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "因为现在我要你去做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "无论你要我做什么，我都答应。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好，你现在就去杀了阿飞。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我早就对你说过，现在还没有到杀他的时候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "现在已到了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "为什么？难道李寻欢已死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "虽还未死，已离死不远。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他……他现在哪里？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "已在我掌握之中。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这几天，我几乎天天晚上跟你在一起，你用什么法子将他抓来的？\n难道你会分身术。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我要的东西，用不着我自己动手，自然会有人送来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "谁送来的？谁有那么大的本事能抓住李寻欢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "龙啸云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错，当然是龙啸云，只有李寻欢的好朋友，才能害得了李寻欢，若想打倒他，无论用什么样的兵器都很困难，只能用情感。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你倒很了解他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我对敌人一向比朋友了解得清楚，譬如说……我就不了解你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我也很明白龙啸云的为人，他绝不会平白无故将李寻欢送来给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他不愿自己杀死李寻欢，所以才借刀杀人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你认为他只有这目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他还想怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他还要我做他的结拜兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这人倒真会占便宜，可是你……你难道答应了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你难道看不出他是想利用你？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "只不过他想得未免太天真了些。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "天真？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他以为做了我的结义兄弟，我就不会动他了，其实，莫说结义兄弟，就算亲兄弟又如何？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错，他可以出卖李寻欢，你自然也可以出卖他。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "龙啸云在我眼中虽一文不值，但他的儿子，却真是个厉害角色。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你见过那小鬼？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这次龙啸云并没有来，是他儿子来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错，那孩子的确是人小鬼大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好，你走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你不想我多留一会儿？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "别的男人跟我在一起，总舍不得离开我，多陪我一刻也是好的，只有你，每次只要一做完事，你就赶我走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "因为我既不是别的男人，也不是你的朋友，我们只不过是在互相利用而已，既然我们心里都很明白，又何必还虚情假意，肉麻当有趣。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "谢谢你，在外面为我们守护，只要知道有你在外面，我就会有种安全感，无论做什么事都愉快得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我还要告诉你个秘密，他年纪虽然大，却还是很强壮，这也许是因为他的经验比别人丰富。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "门是开着的，你自己进来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "带你来的人，已跟你说过价钱了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这价钱比通常高两倍，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "所以你就该听我的话，绝对不能反抗，你懂不懂？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好，你先把衣服脱下来，全脱下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我脱衣服的时候，你不看？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "看女孩子脱衣服，也是种享受，你为什么放弃？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "原来是林阿姨在开小侄的玩笑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "到现在你还要叫我阿姨？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "阿姨总是阿姨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但现在你已是大人了，是吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "才两三年不见，想不到你长得这么快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这两三年来，我们始终打听不出阿姨你的消息，一直都想念得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "但我却听说过你许多事，听说……你对女孩子，比大多数年纪比你大的男人都强得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但在阿姨面前，我还是个孩子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你还叫我阿姨，难道我真的那么老了？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "听说你喜欢的都是小姑娘，而我……我却是个老太婆了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你一点也不老。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "若有人说你老了，那人不是呆子，就是瞎子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你瞎不瞎？呆不呆？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    }
  ],
